txt.en: The uruks of Dol Guldur bear necklaces denoting their loyalty to the Enemy.

'We have found the bodies of our fallen allies butchered...the vile uruks have been taking flesh and sewing it into necklaces, proof of their wretched deeds and their loyalty to the Enemy.\n\n'I will not stand idle with the knowledge that even one of these necklaces remains around their filthy necks! Go to Sâd-en-Dagor and remove them!'
Uruks may be found in Sâd-en-Dagor in Dol Guldur, north-east from Helethir.\n\nStirnir has asked you to collect necklaces from the uruks in Dol Guldur.
'You have done well, [placeholder]. I will rest better knowing these vile fiends paid dearly for their treachery.'
Stirnir is at Helethir, south-west of Dol Guldur.\n\nYou should return to Stirnir for your reward.
'The uruks of Dol Guldur will pay for their treachery!'
'The uruks of Dol Guldur will pay for their treachery!'
